 Now, this is what most people get confused with.

16
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:58,680
 So here it goes.

17
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:04,320
 Most maternity add-ons today cover normal and c-section delivery costs, hospital charges,

18
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:10,360
 room rent, doctor and nursing fees, prenatal checkups, scans, medications, usually 30 to

19
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:15,760
 60 days before delivery, postnatal care and medications, typically 60 to 90 days after

20
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:21,520
 delivery, newborn cover for the first 90 days, NIC cause and sometimes congenital disease

21
